 new price point with its well-established reputation for legendary toughness and durability, I expect it will find a receptive audience in the States.</p><p></p><p></p><p><em>以前</em>：<br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/2021/10/1974-toyota-fj40/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1978 Toyota FJ40</a> (October 29, 2021)</p><p></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317704" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="404" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1.jpeg 1200w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-1024x575.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-768x431.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-250x140.jpeg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317712" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="480" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1.jpeg 980w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1-250x167.jpeg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317705" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="480" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3.jpeg 980w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3-300x200.jpeg 300w, https